<p>Welcome to the Accapitches page! We are&nbsp;a non-auditioned, all girl A capella group. We hold super fun rehearsals every week, and regularly hold themed socials, often jointly with Pitch, Please and Butler Choir.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No auditions, no ability to read music necessary, we simply ask for&nbsp;enthusiasm for rehearsals, performances and socials. As one of Butler's newest societies, we are always open to new ideas, and all songs chosen are voted on by members.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our debut performance at the Societies Garden Party:</p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YuBny8xRJQs">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YuBny8xRJQs</a>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Accapitches Facebook page:</p><p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/861410683923232/?fref=ts">https://www.facebook.com/groups/861410683923232/?fref=ts</a>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>President Facebook pages:</p><p>Anisha:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/anisha.solanki?fref=ts">https://www.facebook.com/anisha.solanki?fref=ts</a>&nbsp;</p><p>Rosie:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/rosiebawn">https://www.facebook.com/rosiebawn</a>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Please do get in touch with any questions&nbsp;and queries you may have!&nbsp;</p><p>Aca-wiedersehen x&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>